OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,GAs far as PR disasters go, they don't
OL,8,Gcome much worse than this.
OL,10,FSTV's proposals to scrap the separate
OL,11,Fnews service for the north of Scotland
OL,12,Fhave attracted huge criticism and
OL,13,Flittle or no support.
OL,15,FThe leaders of all 5 main political
OL,16,Fparties in Scotland signed a letter
OL,17,Fcondemning the proposals.
OL,19,FAberdeen Chamber of Commerce, perhaps
OL,20,Funsurprisingly, is campaigning
OL,21,Fvigorously on the issue.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G1/10
