OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,FBut they also recognise the challenges
OL,8,Ffacing the TV industry.
OL,10,FTheir concern seems to be that the
OL,11,Fcompany is simply intent on making
OL,12,Fmassive cuts, perhaps in direct
OL,13,Fresponse to its immediate financial
OL,14,Fproblems and share price, rather than
OL,15,Fan insistence that the current format
OL,16,Fof the STV News remains fixed in stone.
OL,18,FIf it were not for the immediacy of
OL,19,Fthe situation, that would be an
OL,20,Fimportant issue to consider carefully.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/10
