OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,FThere is no doubt that Grampian's
OL,8,Flegacy endures around the north east
OL,9,Fof Scotland.
OL,11,FThat explains the passion of
OL,12,Fopponents. It is also a credit to the
OL,13,Fcurrent staff and their predecessors.
OL,15,FBut what sort of news service should
OL,16,Fbe provided by STV?
OL,18,FShould it provide a national service
OL,19,Flike BBC Scotland?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/10
