OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,FShould it provide regional news
OL,8,Fprogrammes for distinct parts of
OL,9,FScotland with some Scottish national
OL,10,Fnews included too?
OL,12,FThe actual boundary between STV's two
OL,13,Fareas reflects the transmitter
OL,14,Fcoverage areas.
OL,16,FDo viewers in the Western Isles want a
OL,17,Flocal story from Stonehaven?
OL,19,FDo viewers in Perth ` practically in
OL,20,Fthe Edinburgh commuter zone ` want to
OL,21,Fhear about Shetland?
