OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,FIt's not a straightforward question.
OL,8,FThis is an issue that needs proper
OL,9,Fexamination.
OL,11,FI'm almost beginning to feel sorry for
OL,12,FOfcom. It will be under intense
OL,13,Fpolitical pressure in Scotland over
OL,14,FSTV's proposals.
OL,16,FIt will need to decide whether to
OL,17,Faccept or reject the plan. But it will
OL,18,Falso be mindful of financial realities.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/10
