OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,FIn short, it only has a limited scope
OL,8,Fto impose loss-making legal
OL,9,Fobligations on STV. The value of a
OL,10,FChannel 3 licence is not what it was.
OL,12,FMy guess is a compromise.
OL,14,FSome form of sub-opt will stay.
OL,15,FPerhaps 10 minutes dedicated to the
OL,16,FCentral and North areas within the 6pm
OL,17,Fprogramme and dedicated bulletins at
OL,18,F10.30pm.
