OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,FThe examples elsewhere appear to
OL,8,Fsuggest that Ofcom would have no issue
OL,9,Fwith production and presentation in
OL,10,FGlasgow.
OL,12,FNobody would pretend that the north of
OL,13,Fscotland will get a better local
OL,14,Fservice as a result. But is it the
OL,15,Fbest that can realistically be
OL,16,Fafforded?
OL,18,FHow might STV (which made a loss and
OL,19,Fis barely worth #50m) react if Ofcom
OL,20,Fthrows out its plans completely?
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G8/10
