OL,3,CIs compromise Glasgow-based production/
OL,4,Cpresentation solution best outcome for
OL,5,Cformer Grampian region?
OL,7,FHopefully Ofcom's public consultation
OL,8,Fwill allow all these arguments to be
OL,9,Fvoiced and explored.
OL,11,FThe unions seem able to distinguish
OL,12,Fbetween their members' jobs, their
OL,13,Fconcern for good journalism and simply
OL,14,Fholding on to keeping things the way
OL,15,Fthey were for the sake of doing so.
OL,17,FIt is important to have an informed
OL,18,Fdebate where the choice is not simply
OL,19,Fbetween the end of Grampian and no
OL,20,Fchange at all.
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G9/10
